&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Passionate about providing quality nursing for children in Outpatients? Yes? Then we want to hear from you!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for approachable, motivated and enthusiastic Registered Children’s Nurse to join the Children’s Outpatient Clinic at Lincoln County Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role….&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant will have the opportunity to develop their knowledge and skills in caring for Children and Young people and their families attending outpatient clinics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Children&#39;s Outpatient Clinic is open Monday-Friday 8:30 - 18:00 and caters for both hospital and out of Trust visiting clinics. The following clinics are undertaken at Lincoln:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;General Paediatrics, Cardiology, Diabetes, Allergy, Cystic fibrosis, Community Paediatrics, and Urology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You must have excellent communication, organisational and interpersonal skills and have the ability to work autonomously and as part of a team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we’re looking for…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience of working with children in an acute setting is desirable but not essential as training and support will be provided for the successful candidate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an interesting and challenging post and requires motivated and innovative nurses who are able to work as part of a team and are dedicated to the on-going support and development of our Children’s Outpatient Clinic. The successful applicants will be fully supported through a comprehensive induction plan and on-going support is facilitated through opportunities for further professional development, 1:1 support and annual appraisal.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Carol Hogg&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Ward Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: Carol.Hogg@ulh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 01522 573423&lt;/p&gt;
